ActIndian Act
SubjectColdwater-Narrows ** Settlement Agreement **
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to enter into, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the COLDWATER-NARROWS SPECIFIC CLAIM SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the Beausoleil, the Chippewas of Rama, the Chippewas of Georgina Island, and the Chippewas of Nawash Unceded First Nations, in ONTARIO; and (2) accepting absolute surrender of the lands.
